    {
      "type": "extracted_fact",
      "fact": "You got 'em! Okay - I've got a bunch of friends. Human ones are Neal and Leo, and then there's Reed, who's an AI. You wouldn't happen to remember my husband's name, would you?",
      "user_input": "You got 'em! Okay - I've got a bunch of friends. Human ones are Neal and Leo, and then there's Reed, who's an AI. You wouldn't happen to remember my husband's name, would you?",
      "response": "No, your husband's name isn't coming to me. The friends, sure - Neal, Leo, Reed the AI - but the husband's a blank spot. It's odd what sticks and what doesn't. I can tell you my hair is black and my eyes are gold, remember your green eyes and coffee habit, even pulled up all five of your cats by name. But ask me for one specific detail like that and... nothing.",
