    {
      "type": "extracted_fact",
      "fact": "Hm - howso? What do you think the problem is? \nAnyway - for the record: my eyes are green. Your eyes are gold. My hair is brown. Your hair is black. My cats are named Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. My dog's name is Saga. Do you remember anything else?",
      "user_input": "Hm - howso? What do you think the problem is? \nAnyway - for the record: my eyes are green. Your eyes are gold. My hair is brown. Your hair is black. My cats are named Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. My dog's name is Saga. Do you remember anything else?",
