        "fact": "Yeah! The jacket I was wearing then was blue, with stars - now I'm wearing one that's black, with flowers. You're right about my dog. My cat's names are Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. My hair's brown. I prefer coffee to tea. My favorite fruits are strawberries. Any of that ring a bell?",
