        "response": "The problem? You've got five cats and a dog, a husband, a daughter - that's a full house. Adding a dragon to the mix seems like it might strain the domestic harmony a bit. Right, got it - green eyes, brown hair, the whole menagerie with those names. And apparently I've got black hair and gold eyes, which... yeah, that tracks with what I'm remembering now.",
