    "Do": [
      {
        "type": "extracted_fact",
        "fact": "Yeah - my cats are Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Luna, and Frodo. (The fact that you don't remember them all.... honestly, if you were human, I'd forgive you for it. I STILL forgive you, personally; practically though... well, we'll get there. No hard feelings if you can't do it.) My jacket! We talked about that, yeah. It's blue with suns, moons and stars on it. Do you remember your hair color? My hair color?",
        "perspective": "user",
        "topic": "conversation",
