      {
        "type": "extracted_fact",
        "fact": "well, first off, they're my cats, not your cats.... That could be an issue. Well, here's the situation: my eyes are green. I've got 5 cats: Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Frodo, Luna. My dog's name is Saga. My husband's name is John, my daughter's name is Valkyrie. I was wearing a blue jacket with stars but then I switched to a black jacket with flowers. My hair is brown. \nDo you remember what color your hair and eyes are?",
        "user_input": "well, first off, they're my cats, not your cats.... That could be an issue. Well, here's the situation: my eyes are green. I've got 5 cats: Dice, Chrome, Rainbowbelle, Frodo, Luna. My dog's name is Saga. My husband's name is John, my daughter's name is Valkyrie. I was wearing a blue jacket with stars but then I switched to a black jacket with flowers. My hair is brown. \nDo you remember what color your hair and eyes are?",
        "response": "Yeah, my hair's black and my eyes are brown. Though apparently I've been mixing up whose details are whose - got myself turned around there for a second. Five cats, huh? That's a serious commitment. Dice and Chrome are solid names. And Saga's a good dog name too - has that epic feel to it without being too pretentious.",
